Running the Project


1)  Backend Services
To start backend services, 
navigate to the folder infrastructure/ and run:
docker compose down
docker compose up --build


2)  Frontend
The frontend runs via Docker.
From the root of the frontend directory, execute:
docker build -t ft_transcendence_frontend .
docker run -p 8080:80 ft_transcendence_frontend

3) Then open your browser and go to:
http://localhost:8080



CLI USAGE (when backend and frontend are running)
- to start the game:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/game/start -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"leftPlayer": { "alias": "Alice", "id": "44" },"rightPlayer": { "alias": "Bob", "id": "66" },"matchId": 1,"type": "CONSOLE"}'

- to stop the game:
curl http://localhost:3000/game/stop   

- to move paddles: 
  - left Player down:
    curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/game/move -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"whichPlayer": "left","dir": "down"}'
  - left Player up:
    curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/game/move -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"whichPlayer": "left","dir": "up"}'
  - left Player stop moving:
    curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/game/move -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"whichPlayer": "left","dir": "stop"}'
  - right Player down:
      curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/game/move -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"whichPlayer": "right","dir": "down"}'
  - right Player up:
      curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/game/move -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"whichPlayer": "right","dir": "up"}'
  - right Player stop moving:
      curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/game/move -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"whichPlayer": "right","dir": "stop"}'
